response.overview: This was recorded a few days before her Tokyo performance ("NEO GRAND" co-hosted by Minna no Kimochi, AVYSS and Local World) when she first came to Japan in 2024 to support AVYSS. She expressed a desire to film a DJ video in an unusual location in Japan, so after discussing the content, they rented a room and filmed it.
response.tagline: A live set by Australian Electronic Producer Ninajirachi
response.title: Ninajirachi | JAPANESE OTAKU ROOM (FULL SET)
